"Are you sure you want to go back to the main view? This will start a new "
"game."
msgstr "Stvarno se želiš vratiti na glavni prikaz? To će započeti novu igru."

#: src/alert-dialogs.js:65
msgid "Go Back"
msgstr "Idi natrag"

#: src/how-to-play.js:5
msgid "The Rules"
msgstr "Pravila"

#: src/how-to-play.js:8
msgid ""
"Create words using the <span weight=\"ultrabold\">provided letters</span>"
msgstr "Stvori riječi koristeći <span weight=\"ultrabold\">zadana slova</span>"

#: src/how-to-play.js:9
msgid ""
"The words <span weight=\"ultrabold\">must contain at least 4 letters</span>"
msgstr ""
"Riječi <span weight=\"ultrabold\">moraju sadržavati barem 4 slova</span>"

#: src/how-to-play.js:10
msgid ""
"Each word <span weight=\"ultrabold\">must include the center letter</span>"
msgstr ""
"Svaka riječ <span weight=\"ultrabold\">mora sadržavati središnje slovo</span>"

#: src/how-to-play.js:11
msgid ""
"Provided <span weight=\"ultrabold\">letters can be used more than once</span>"
msgstr ""
"Zadana <span weight=\"ultrabold\">slova se mogu koristiti više puta</span>"

#: src/how-to-play.js:15
msgid "The Scores"
msgstr "Rezultati"

#: src/how-to-play.js:18
msgid ""
"Each <span weight=\"ultrabold\">four-letter</span> word is worth <span  "
"weight=\"ultrabold\">one point</span>"
msgstr ""
"Svaka riječ <span weight=\"ultrabold\">od četiri slova</span> vrijedi <span  "
"weight=\"ultrabold\">jedan bod</span>"

#: src/how-to-play.js:19
msgid ""
"<span weight=\"ultrabold\">Longer words</span> earn <span "
"weight=\"ultrabold\">one point per letter</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span weight=\"ultrabold\">Dulje riječi</span> donose <span "
"weight=\"ultrabold\">jedan bod po slovu</span>"

#: src/how-to-play.js:20
msgid ""
"Words containing <span weight=\"ultrabold\">all the letters</span> earn "
"<span weight=\"ultrabold\">seven additional points</span>"
msgstr ""
"Riječi koje sadržavaju <span weight=\"ultrabold\">sva slova</span> donose "
"<span weight=\"ultrabold\">sedam dodatnih bodova</span>"

#: src/how-to-play.js:23
msgid "About Hints"
msgstr "O savjetima"

#: src/how-to-play.js:26
msgid ""
"The symbol, <span weight=\"ultrabold\">Σ</span>, is short for <span "
"weight=\"ultrabold\">sum</span>"
msgstr ""
"Simbol <span weight=\"ultrabold\">Σ</span> je skraćenica za <span "
"weight=\"ultrabold\">zbroj</span>"

#: src/how-to-play.js:27
msgid ""
"The <span weight=\"ultrabold\">first column</span> contains the provided "
"letters eg E, K, L, etc"
msgstr ""
"<span weight=\"ultrabold\">Prvi stupac</span> sadržava navedena slova, npr. "
"E, K, L itd."

#: src/how-to-play.js:28
msgid ""
"The <span weight=\"ultrabold\">last column</span> contains the total number "
"of words that begin with the corresponding letter"
msgstr ""
"<span weight=\"ultrabold\">Zadnji stupac</span> sadržava ukupan broj riječi "
"koje počinju s odgovarajućim slovom"

#: src/how-to-play.js:29
msgid ""
"The <span weight=\"ultrabold\">first row</span> contains the word lengths "
"e.g. 4 letters, 5 letters, etc"
msgstr ""
"<span weight=\"ultrabold\">Prvi red</span> sadržava duljine riječi, npr. 4 "
"slova, 5 slova itd."

#: src/how-to-play.js:30
msgid ""
"The <span weight=\"ultrabold\">last row</span> contains the total number of "
"4-letter words, 5-letter words, etc"
msgstr ""
"<span weight=\"ultrabold\">Zadnji redak</span> sadržava ukupan broj riječi s "
"4 slova, riječi s 5 slova itd."

#: src/how-to-play.js:31
msgid ""
"The <span weight=\"ultrabold\">non-edge(inner) table cells</span> contain "
"the number of n-letter words that begin with a particular letter"
msgstr ""
"<span weight=\"ultrabold\">Ne-rubna (unutarnja) polja tablice</span> "
"sadržavaju broj riječi s n brojem slova koje počinju s određenim slovom"

#: src/how-to-play.js:32
msgid ""
"The <span weight=\"ultrabold\">two-letter list</span> contains the number of "
"words that begin with the given pair of letters e.g. DE-20 means 20 words "
"begin with the letters DE"
msgstr ""
"<span weight=\"ultrabold\">Dvoslovni popis</span> sadržava broj riječi koje "
"počinju sa zadanim parom slova, npr. DE-20 znači da 20 riječi počinju sa "
"slovima DE"

